OL,3,CSenedd votes on new rules about
OL,4,Cpromoting foods linked to obesity
OL,6,FNew rules about how and where foods
OL,7,Fhigh in fat, salt and sugar can be
OL,8,Fpromoted and displayed in larger shops
OL,9,Fand online have been passed by the
OL,10,FSenedd.
OL,12,FThe regulations are designed to
OL,13,Fprevent impulse purchases and over-
OL,14,Fconsumption and will help to tackle
OL,15,Fthe growing problem of obesity in
OL,16,FWales.The Food (Promotion and
OL,17,FPresentation) (Wales) Regulations
OL,18,F2025, which largely mirror rules
OL,19,Falready in place in England, will:
