OL,3,CSenedd votes on new rules about
OL,4,Cpromoting foods linked to obesity
OL,6,FResearch shows up to 83% of purchases
OL,7,Fmade on promotion are impulse buys.
OL,8,FAnd almost half (43%) of food and
OL,9,Fdrink products in prominent store
OL,10,Flocations promote sugary foods and
OL,11,Fdrinks.
OL,13,FAfter the vote Health Secretary Jeremy
OL,14,FMiles said: "These regulations are a
OL,15,Fkey part of our strategy to tackle
OL,16,FWales' growing obesity problem.
OL,18,F"I'm pleased they have been approved
OL,19,Fby the Senedd, as they will have a
OL,20,Fsignificant impact on the health of
OL,21,Four nation for years to come.
